subject: Fire insurance -- Ontario -- St. Catharines; Fire risk assessment -- Ontario -- St. Catharines; Real property -- Ontario -- St. Catharines; St. Catharines (Ont.)
description: The fire insurance plan for St. Catharines, Ontario, surveyed July 1901 and revised to January 1913. The revisions have been pasted on. The plan consists of: title sheet (includes index to streets, specials, blocks), sheet 1 (key plan, scale [1:6,000]), sheets 2-39. Call No. FC 3155.175 G62 1913.
